{"tid":1074390,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)女拳霸 又又又又又又邊個殺我隻狗1-2 三重威脅","createTime":"2019-03-23T10:57:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-23T13:56:30.000Z","uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"9b5fdeaf208d1416c6c970bbecabd3d0336b7ef4","tid":1074390,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T10:57:20.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=INFrb%2BpCZNVkt1J9J2ljEPS0i%2BS8%2FYHgnNJfWlbrK%2Bw%3D&h=6325b902\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台 順便開返個FLASHPLAYER<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=INFrb%2BpCZNVkt1J9J2ljEPS0i%2BS8%2FYHgnNJfWlbrK%2Bw%3D&h=f51af49b\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有OKRU睇<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg&d=INFrb%2BpCZNVkt1J9J2ljEPS0i%2BS8%2FYHgnNJfWlbrK%2Bw%3D&h=9821ef06\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg</a> &lt;GOOGLE睇唔到解決方法好似係 BY伯爵 <br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/0/05/Chocolate_2008_poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fen%2F0%2F05%2FChocolate_2008_poster.jpg&h=c05198b2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DYuhXZ_XkAIuNVm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDYuhXZ_XkAIuNVm.jpg&h=62ceec90&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/3/37/Triple_Threat_Poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F3%2F37%2FTriple_Threat_Poster.jpg&h=5f2388ee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.自閉症少女雪（Sen，琴嘉飾）自小與母親珊本（Sin）相依為命。珊本為泰國黑幫頭目八哥的手下，因與日本黑幫頭目岸本（Masashi，阿部寬飾）相戀，兩人被泰國黑道中人視為眼中釘，誓要除之而後快。岸本為保性命，不得已回歸日本。珊本母女四處逃避，卻依然難逃黑幫魔掌<br />\n<br />\n2.約翰&middot;維克是一位退隱江湖的殺手，不久前失去了因病而逝的妻子海倫，這令他哀傷不已，舉辦完葬禮後連過去同為殺手的馬克斯也前來關心他。不久後，約翰收到了一隻海倫生前為他訂的小狗黛西，海倫希望黛西能陪伴約翰，而他也將黛西視為朋友。一早，約翰開著他69年的福特野馬愛車和黛西出門，當到一間加油站加油時，塔拉索夫家族的領頭維果的兒子約謝夫想要和約翰買下他的車，但被約翰拒絕，約謝夫便此心生不滿。當晚，約謝夫和另外兩位朋友格雷戈里、維克多蒙面闖入約翰家中，不但襲擊了他還殺死了黛西，之後便搶了車庫裡的福特野馬後離開。約翰從昏迷中醒來後發現奄奄一息的黛西爬到了自己的身旁斷了氣，之後便將牠埋於後院<br />\n<br />\n3.在前殺手約翰&middot;維克殺光維果和約謝夫&middot;塔拉索夫一行人的四天後，約翰開始尋找自己遭到前者搶走的1969年福特野馬，並循跡發現車在維果的弟弟艾倫那裡。約翰在獲得艾倫根據地的門卡後隨即開車前往，並與艾倫的手下們展開飛車追逐及搏鬥，而艾倫也察覺到傳說中「殺神」的到來；在他打倒其手下後，約翰到艾倫的辦公室倒了兩杯酒給他，以示「和平」。接著約翰便開車回家，與自己在殺死維果後帶回家的「沒有取名」狗見面..<br />\n<br />\n4.故事敘述一名億萬富翁的女兒意外遭到了犯罪集團鎖定為頭號目標，而能夠保護她的是三名不同國家、目標和武術的打手，這使得雙方即將展開了一場腥風血雨的暴力戰役..<br />\n<br />\n7 00PM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=INFrb%2BpCZNVkt1J9J2ljEPS0i%2BS8%2FYHgnNJfWlbrK%2Bw%3D&h=86f4f40e\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=INFrb%2BpCZNVkt1J9J2ljEPS0i%2BS8%2FYHgnNJfWlbrK%2Bw%3D&h=30cd8eb3\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67d7921cd02caea1d95ce504dc3621d4bcbe5968","tid":1074390,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T10:57:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"916da54a95d146a4049b60dc8552f443edfec77a","tid":1074390,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T11:38:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dae89dcc222c17c563a2dbb5cdc7dec1b683b260","tid":1074390,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T12:37:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"781ad86e774f2f428dd2500396106cefc9881b33","tid":1074390,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T13:56:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}